Grenevia jest ogniwem łączącym inwestorów z zieloną transformacją. Wspieramy perspektywiczne projekty, które zmieniają przemysł i pomagają budować niskoemisyjną gospodarkę. 

Wywodzimy się z tradycyjnego przemysłu. W ostatnich 20 latach zrealizowaliśmy kilkanaście projektów M&A oraz stworzyliśmy globalną markę. To doświadczenie wykorzystaliśmy do wdrożenia nowej strategii rozwoju i przemiany w Grenevię – spółki integrującej i rozwijającej działalność czterech segmentów biznesowych:
fotowoltaika wielkoskalowa i rozwiązania PV dla biznesu  Projekt Solartechnik; 
systemy bateryjne, magazyny energii i elektromobilność  IMPACT Clean Power Technology; 
rozwiązania z zakresu automatyki dla przemysłu i dla sektora dystrybucji energii  Elgór+Hansen;
technologie i produkty dla sektora wydobywczego i energetyki wiatrowej  FAMUR. 

Grenevia is a link connecting investors with the green transformation. We support prospective projects that change the industry and help build a low-emission economy. 

We originate from the traditional industry. In the last 20 years, we have completed several M&A projects and created a global brand. We have used this experience to implement a new development strategy and transform into Grenevia - a company integrating and developing the activities of four business segments:
 large-scale photovoltaics and PV solutions for business  Projekt Solartechnik; 
 battery systems, energy storage and e-mobility  IMPACT Clean Power Technology; 
 solutions for industrial automation and energy distribution sector  Elgór+Hansen;
 technologies and products for the mining and wind energy sectors  FAMUR.

Founded in Genoa in 1895, for over 120 years Coeclerici has been a reference point in commodity supplies for the steel and chemical industries. Today, thanks to this consolidated business experience, it is the leading company of a Group present in two business area, energy and industry, with high added value, with a constant diversification activity and a strategic-financial model aimed at development through acquisitions and organic growth. Coeclerici S.p.A. is the Group’s holding company, coordinating and supporting Group activities in 12 countries around the world. Characterised by a strong international vocation, the Group has been lead since 1992 by the Chairman and CEO Paolo Clerici, and operates through three highly specialized business units:
• Mining division, which deals with the extraction of energy coal from its own mines located in the Kemerovo Region (Russia);
• Trading division, which operates mainly in the marketing of raw materials such as coal, anthracite, coke and iron ore, serving a network of clients in over 25 countries;
• Industry division, established at the beginning of 2017 with the acquisition of IMS Deltamatic, now IMS Technologies, one of the world’s leading operators in the production of high-tech industrial machinery and plants for the converting and packaging industries.
The Group is continuing the process of diversification of its business, with an industrial approach and great ability for innovation.

Holding company of Kamida group of companies working in transportation, logistics, services for agriculture industry, real estate development, labor rental and outsourcing. Companies employ more than 600 people. 

The Kamida Group holding currently consists of the following companies:
KAMIDA GROUP, UAB is an internal service center that provides business support and development services (accounting, finance, IT, HR, legal support, purchasing and sales management and etc.) to all companies belonging to the Kamida Group holding;
KAMIDA, UAB - international cargo transportation services in Western Europe;
KAMIDA LOGISTICS, UAB – forwarding, warehouse logistics services and work for carriers;
KAMIDA TRANSPORTE, GMBH - forwarding, warehouse logistics services and transportation organization (Germany);
KLOVIMA, UAB – rental of agricultural equipment, sale of equipment, sowing and harvesting service with an operator, as well as oversized, non-standard, heavy cargo transportation services;
KLOVIMA, SIA - rental and sale of agricultural machinery in Latvia, grain harvesting service with an operator (Latvia).
KLOVIMA UKRAINE, RAB - rental and sale of agricultural machinery in Ukraine (operations and activity are currently suspended);
KAMIDA AGRO, RAB - sale of agricultural machinery in Ukraine (operations and activity are currently suspended);
KAMIDA NT, UAB – real estate rental, development and sale of new projects, investment;
KAMIDA SERVICES, UAB – selection and supply service of various professional specialists for partners in European countries;
SELECTAS EU, UAB - selection and supply services of various professional specialists for foreign clients and internal group companies;

AC Health Pharma is an integrated pharma network wholly-owned by AC Health – the healthcare arm of Ayala Corporation.

Our portfolio spans across the pharmaceutical value chain:
Generika Drugstore, the pioneer in generic retail pharmacies that provide Filipinos options across price points;
I.E. Medica and MedEthix, a major pharmaceutical importer-distributor pair that bring in innovative products and;
St. Joseph Drug, a leading pharmaceutical retail chain in North Luzon.

We work with our partners to make quality medicines and health essentials more affordable and accessible to Transform Health for Every Filipino.

Riza Solutions

A Riza Solutions foi concebida para também ser diferente, provendo as melhores soluções de dívida, via Project Finance ou Corporate Finance, mezanino, equity e M&A para os clientes da Riza Asset. A assessoria financeira conta com:

I. Um profundo conhecimento setorial nas verticais de atuação da Riza, especialmente infraestrutura e energia, agronegócio e imobiliário;
II. Experiência e criatividade na formatação dessas soluções em transações complexas;
III. Rede consolidada de relacionamento com o mercado de capitais em geral, mas também com bancos comerciais, multilaterais, bancos de desenvolvimento, além de investidores institucionais, fundações, private banking e family offices.

