Setting up and chairing supervisory & non-executive boards that are equipped to drive growth, to acquire investments, and to exit.
We are a network of professionals helping entrepreneurs develop growth strategies, to execute these strategies, to connect to exclusive networks, to investors, and to exit. We do this in the role of chairman/chairwoman of the supervisory or non-executive board.
Examples of activities:
-	Set up new companies, including governance boards;
-	Develop competitive value propositions for customers, investors, and business partners;
-	Strengthen the CEO, CFO, or COO in their roles;
-	Connect with exclusive networks. 
Together, we make this journey and keep supporting you as a supervisory or non-executive board chair.

